data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in Hartville with over 1800 sq. ft. Enjoy the open floor plan that allows you to entertain your guests & family as you prepare your meals in the updated kitchen that offers plenty of cabinet & counter space. Have you family/friend holiday dinners in the large eat in kitchen. Relax in the cozy, spacious living room & have a guest full bathroom on the main floor. Unwind after a long day on the front porch or on the back patio that has a fenced in backyard for privacy. Utilize the built in storage area on the 2nd floor with 3 large bedrooms with wonderful closet space. This home has many updated throughout. A new roof & furnace was installed about 5 years ago. Schedule your showing today, so you can move in, unpack & make this your home sweet home.
